    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h3 id="本文仅针对nexT最新版本8-0-0进行优化"><a href="#本文仅针对nexT最新版本8-0-0进行优化" class="headerlink" title="本文仅针对nexT最新版本8.0.0进行优化"></a>本文仅针对nexT最新版本8.0.0进行优化</h3><h3 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h3><ul><li><p>安装<a href="https://nodejs.org/">node</a>,[git](<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p></li><li><p>注册<a href="https://github.com/">github</a>并登陆,创建代码仓库,名为:用户名.github.io</p></li></ul><p>进入命令行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>cd到一个目录,然后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时,hexo在<a href="127.0.0.1:4000">127.0.0.1:4000</a>运行</p><ul><li>也可以用<code>p=</code>来指定端口,如</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s p&#x3D;8080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时hexo在127.0.0.1:8080运行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-theme-next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者git clone</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
